<F P=102>  AU1403180494 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1700 
GMT 14 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU1403180494 </F>
<F P=104>  Sofia Khorizont Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Bulgarian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] An agreement on political cooperation and allied 
relations between the Bulgarian Social Democratic Party [BSDP] 
and the Civic Alliance for the Republic [GOR] was signed on 14 
March by the two party leaders, Dr. Petur Dertliev and 
Aleksandur Tomov. 
  Assuming the mutual commitment to act for the construction 
of 
a political alternative of the confrontation bipolar model, the 
two formations express confidence that their cooperation will 
contribute to the democratic development of society and 
improving political life in Bulgaria. 

