<F P=106> [TA SR report: "Another Deputy Expelled"] </F>
  [Text] Bratislava--The Movement for a Democratic Slovakia 
[HZDS] Municipal District Presidium at Strecnianska Street in 
Bratislava 5 decided on 9 March to terminate the HZDS membership 
of Vladimir Bajan, deputy to the National Council of the Slovak 
Republic [NRSR]. The Municipal District Presidium expressed full 
support for the prime minister and the government of the Slovak 
Republic and for the NRSR chairman. 

