Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Prague, March 16 (CTK) -- Julius Brocka was today 
appointed the new Slovak minister for employment and social 
affairs. Brocka was proposed by the Christian Democratic 
Movement (KDH). 
  He was born on January 1, 1957 and studied at the 
Engineering 
Faculty of the Slovak Technical University in Bratislava. He 
