ministers, including the formal swearing-in ceremony. 
  [Samel] [passage omitted] Jan Findra, head of the 
presidential office, read out a statement in which the president 
appointed Jozef Moravcik as the prime minister of the Slovak 
Republic and chairman of the State Defense Council. He also 
appointed Brigita Schmognerova as deputy prime minister 
responsible for economic and political transformation, Roman 
Kovac as deputy prime minister responsible for noneconomic 
